<英文法規名稱>Regulations Governing Disposal and Sales through Open Tender of the Old Quarters for Military Dependents and National Land Not Fitting the Used of Military Camps</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>國軍老舊眷村及不適用營地之國有土地標售或處分辦法</中文法規名稱>
